rained, living human soul, cultivated and strengthened by long study and thought, that breathes the real breath of life into boys and girls and makes them human, whether they be black or white, Greek, Russian or American.', 3227, 0), (492796, 'Violence and arms can never resolve the problems of men.', 66871, 0), (492797, 'Strong beliefs win strong men, and then make them stronger.', 424, 0), (492798, 'Elegance is always in style for men. There are all different kinds of elegance. It can be silk, it can be a T-shirt.', 21473, 0), (492799, 'I directed the men in our barque to approach near the savages, and hold their arms in readiness to do their duty in case they notice any movement of these people against us.', 75893, 0), (492800, 'Every man needs two women: a quiet home-maker, and a thrilling nymph.', 210, 0);
