INSERT INTO quotes (id, content, author_id, views) VALUES (493051, 'Men are freest when they are most unconscious of freedom. The shout is a rattling of chains, always was.', 178, 0), (493052, 'In life we shall find many men that are great, and some that are good, but very few men that are both great and good.', 432, 0), (493053, 'Men''s arguments often prove nothing but their wishes.', 432, 0), (493054, 'The country is filled with energetic and enterprising men, rendered desperate by being reduced from affluence to poverty through the vicissitudes of the times. They will give an impulse to smuggling unknown to the country heretofore.', 63147, 0), (493055, 'On this shrunken globe, men can no longer live as strangers.', 69260, 0), (493056, 'One must judge men not by their opinions, but by what their opinions have made of them.', 68283, 0), (493057, 'Whatever crushes individuality is despotism, by whatever name it may be called and whether it professes to be enforcing the will of God or the injunctions of men.', 1880, 0), (493058, 'Men tend to feel threatened women tend to feel guilty. ', 12361, 0), (493059, 'What is the most beautiful in virile men is something feminine what is most beautiful in feminine women is something masculine. ', 4673, 0), (493060, 'Boys will be boys, and so will a lot of middle-aged men.', 14120, 0), (493061, 'All men were made by the Great Spirit Chief. They are all brothers.', 4664, 0), (493062, 'There is always a type of man who says he loves his fellow men, and expects to make a living at it.', 13154, 0), (493063, 'Men have as exaggerated an idea of their rights as women have of their wrongs.', 13154, 0), (493064, 'Lonely women destroy themselves lonely men threaten the world. ', 28809, 0), (493065, 'It is only the great men who are truly obscene. If they had not dared to be obscene, they could never have dared to be great.', 62533, 0), (493066, 'It is easier to lead men to combat, stirring up their passion, than to restrain them and direct them toward the patient labors of peace.', 8, 0), (493067, 'When two men in business always agree, one of them is unnecessary.', 8630, 0), (493068, 'Life, in my estimation, is a biological misadventure that we terminate on the shoulders of six strange men whose only objective is to make a hole in one with you.', 13077, 0), (493069, 'Whatever makes men good Christians, makes them good citizens.', 3308, 0), (493070, 'Men may live fools, but fools they cannot die.', 4028, 0), (493071, 'Men, even when alone, lighten their labors by song, however rude it may be.', 63010, 0), (493072, 'Men tire themselves in pursuit of rest.', 1719, 0), (493073, 'Homosexuality in Russia is a crime and the punishment is seven years in prison, locked up with the other men. There is a three year waiting list.', 65730, 0), (493074, 'Every man is a volume if you know how to read him.', 3573, 0), (493075, 'Men are actually the weaker sex.', 10494, 0), (493076, 'A lot of times, women don''t get the male perspective in regards to a relationship, what men go through when they''re not really dealing well.', 73393, 0), (493077, 'Italian men do appreciate beautiful women. They''re not afraid of the beauty, which is nice.', 70744, 0), (493078, 'All men have an instinct for conflict: at least, all healthy men.', 4439, 0), (493079, 'Women thrive on novelty and are easy meat for the commerce of fashion. Men prefer old pipes and torn jackets.', 1132, 0), (493080, 'Culture makes all men gentle.', 31012, 0), (493081, 'Like all young men I set out to be a genius, but mercifully laughter intervened.', 6034, 0), (493082, 'First find the man in yourself if you will inspire manliness in others.', 13866, 0), (493083, 'There will always be men struggling to change, and there will always be those who are controlled by the past.', 73712, 0), (493084, 'For most men life is a search for the proper manila envelope in which to get themselves filed.', 8863, 0), (493085, 'Whenever ideas fail, men invent words.', 21353,